channel.title: How to get windows software keys!
channel.description:
[center][b]How to get most windows software keys![/b][/center]
There is a program I came across the other day, It is really handy!
It will generate keys for:
Windows Xp Pro Windows Xp Corp Windows Xp Home Office Xp Pro/Plus Visio Xp Pro
It will take around 30 searches to find a valid key (Sorry but you have to wait a while for a valid one, About 30mins)
I did make one valid key:
Results of Search finished on: 08/15/06, 13:52:23
Software: WiNDOWS XP PRO
Max. Searches: 50 Keys processed: 31 Num. Keys to find: 1 Valid Keys found: 1
Operation completed successfully !
Found Keys: 4P2H3-2G3G6-PB6CJ-8QWGW-GH69J
This was found on demonoid, I can't/won't take any credit for this program and I am in no way responsible if anything happense to your computer/legaly.
This is for learning purposes only and should not be used to make keys for microsoft products! Use at your own risk!
And your welcome :D
MoO
